'''佛罗里达大道'''（Florida Avenue）是[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]的一条主要干道。它原名界限街（Boundary Street），因为它原是首都的东北边界，城市发展后越出原有边界，于是在1890年改名为佛罗里达大道。<ref>{{cite news|title=Boundary Street No longer; it Will Be Known as Florida Avenue in the Future|newspaper=The Washington Post|date=January 15, 1890|page=8}}</ref>

佛罗里达大道的西端在马萨诸塞大道、22街和 Q街，东端在H街、15街、马里兰大道、贝宁路和勃兰登堡路交汇的Starburst 广场<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/washington/blog/2014/09/new-gateway-to-h-street-ne-mixed-use-building.html|last=Neibauer|first=Michael|title=New Gateway to H Street NE? Mixed-Use Building Proposed for Site Next to Starburst Intersection|newspaper=Washington Business Journal|date=September 29, 2014|accessdate=September 30, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003032929/http://www.bizjournals.com/washington/blog/2014/09/new-gateway-to-h-street-ne-mixed-use-building.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

